===Proper Noun===
'''Jedi'''

A fictional order of beings from George Lucas'''[[w:Star_Wars|Star Wars]]'' universe who are gifted with heightened sensitivity to and awareness of "The Force." According to the "prequel" films, the Jedi are those beings who are most highly infested by the "midichlorians" - microbial symbiotes that communicate the "will of the Force" to the Jedi adept.

